# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in with your values:

```bash
# Network configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_NETWORK=mainnet
# Options: mainnet, testnet

# RPC Endpoints (public endpoints work fine)
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://forno.celo.org
NEXT_PUBLIC_TESTNET_RPC_URL=https://alfajores-forno.celo-testnet.org

# Optional: Your backend API for leaderboard
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Optional: Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_ID=
```

## Notes

- All `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` variables are exposed to the browser
- No sensitive keys should be included (private keys, API secrets)
- For local testing with ngrok, use the ngrok URL instead of localhost:3000
